Package ba.unsa.etf.rpr.controllers

Class AdminTicketsController

java.lang.Object
ba.unsa.etf.rpr.controllers.AdminTicketsController
public class AdminTicketsController extends Object
AdminTicketsController is a JavaFX Controller class that implements the functionalities of adding, updating, and deleting Tickets objects in the database. It contains several GUI components such as TextFields, ListView, and ChoiceBox to allow the user to input, view, and modify the ticket information. The class also has a method for calculating the ticket price based on the chosen travel class and flight.
